<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Sony's Columbia
   Revives TriStar
   Television Unit
   ----
   By Kevin Goldman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
10/08/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7
</SO>
